#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.arctan.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.arctan"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:1 of
msgid "Trigonometric inverse tangent, element-wise."
msgstr "三角反正切函数，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:3 of
msgid "The inverse of tan, so that if ``y = tan(x)`` then ``x = arctan(y)``."
msgstr "tan 的反函数，即如果 ``y = tan(x)``，那么 ``x = arctan(y)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。一个元组（只能作为关键字"
"参数）必须长度等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:17 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Out has the same shape as `x`.  Its real part is in ``[-pi/2, "
"pi/2]`` (``arctan(+/-inf)`` returns ``+/-pi/2``). It is a scalar if `x` "
"is a scalar."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 输出与 `x` 具有相同的形状。其实部在 ``[-pi/2, pi/2]`` 范围内（"
"``arctan(+/-inf)`` 返回 ``+/-pi/2``）。如果 `x` 是标量，则输出也为标量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`arctan2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:25 of
msgid ""
"The \"four quadrant\" arctan of the angle formed by (`x`, `y`) and the "
"positive `x`-axis."
msgstr "由 (`x`, `y`) 和正 `x` 轴所形成角度的“四象限”反正切值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`angle`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:28 of
msgid "Argument of complex values."
msgstr "复数值的幅角。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:31 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:32 of
msgid ""
"`arctan` is a multi-valued function: for each `x` there are infinitely "
"many numbers `z` such that tan(`z`) = `x`.  The convention is to return "
"the angle `z` whose real part lies in [-pi/2, pi/2]."
msgstr ""
"`arctan` 是一个多值函数：对于每个 `x`，有无穷多个数字 `z` 使得 tan(`z`) ="
" `x`。约定返回其实部位于 [-pi/2, pi/2] 范围内的角度 `z`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:36 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `arctan` always returns real output. "
"For each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"yields ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数输入数据类型，`arctan` 总是返回实数输出。对于无法表示为实数或"
"无穷大的值，它会返回 ``nan`` 并设置 `invalid` 浮点数错误标志。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:40 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `arctan` is a complex analytic function that "
"has [`1j, infj`] and [`-1j, -infj`] as branch cuts, and is continuous "
"from the left on the former and from the right on the latter."
msgstr ""
"对于复数输入，`arctan` 是一个复解析函数，其分支切割为 [`1j, infj`] 和 [`-"
"1j, -infj`]，并在前者的左侧和后者的右侧连续。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:44 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "The inverse tangent is also known as `atan` or tan^{-1}."
msgstr "反正切函数也称为 `atan` 或 tan^{-1}。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:47 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:48 of
msgid ""
"Abramowitz, M. and Stegun, I. A., *Handbook of Mathematical Functions*, "
"10th printing, New York: Dover, 1964, pp. 79. "
"http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"Abramowitz, M. 和 Stegun, I. A.，《数学函数手册》，第10版，纽约：Dover，"
"1964年，第79页。http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:53 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.arctan.arctan:54 of
msgid ""
"We expect the arctan of 0 to be 0, and of 1 to be pi/4: >>> import "
"maxframe.tensor as mt"
msgstr ""
"我们期望 0 的反正切值为 0，1 的反切值为 pi/4：>>> import maxframe.tensor "
"as mt"

